{"tid":720891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[港女柒到爆] 一名港女苦主，上月被氹送厚禮，人渣食過翻尋味，又再出動.........","createTime":"2018-06-28T09:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T14:30:39.000Z","uid":83048,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"60cb4513e09ec580a084f80a537c9be214f8d44d","tid":720891,"uid":83048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xRgdkPzeGa0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxRgdkPzeGa0&d=ru7BXlD9JOrC8aP0jmFt%2FIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b11c7e84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xRgdkPzeGa0</a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xRgdkPzeGa0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxRgdkPzeGa0&d=ru7BXlD9JOrC8aP0jmFt%2FIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b11c7e84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xRgdkPzeGa0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n苦主Helen在上月透過交友app認識柏圖，經過一段時間的短訊溝通，柏圖終於出擊邀約Helen見面，再以同一個劇本，生日送禮物環節，成功氹到Helen送上2000元現金，「佢話要揾相熟朋友做西裝，打比朋友時仲話係未來女朋友送。」奸計得逞，渣男柏圖甚至提出更大膽要求，要求生日飯折現，結果Helen再次乖乖奉上500大元，最後換來柏圖請她吃了一頓餃子晚飯。<br />\n<br />\n一個月後，柏圖食過翻尋味，提出約會，Helen配合記者放蛇，再約對方見面。   甫見面，柏圖即送上手鏈，透露此乃母親意思，及後着Helen回禮，目標希望能送贈Apple產品予愛好打機的父母。 <br />\n<br />\n甫見面，柏圖即送上手鏈，透露此乃母親意思，及後着Helen回禮，目標希望能送贈Apple產品予愛好打機的父母。<br />\n<br />\n記者上前踢爆，問柏圖為何經常以生日為由氹人送禮，柏圖聞言即拔足狂奔，落荒而逃。"},{"pid":"0e5bb259c410fd8b5b31e8e352b29570a761105a","tid":720891,"uid":83048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pvYJ3LC84pg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpvYJ3LC84pg&d=ru7BXlD9JOrC8aP0jmFt%2FIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=286f9c16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pvYJ3LC84pg</a>"},{"pid":"1cdafe7fde92352524a78e014a3607f1c2888718","tid":720891,"uid":83048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0